    "section": "",
    "content": "<!-- ⬇️ TARJETA DE VÍDEO (Google Drive) -->\n<div class=\"drive-video-card\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Demostración de cierre en INVENTORY\">\n  <div class=\"drive-video-card__body\">\n    <div class=\"drive-video-card__text\">\n      <h3 class=\"drive-video-card__title\">Demostración completa: cierre/apertura en INVENTORY</h3>\n      <p class=\"drive-video-card__desc\">\n        Vídeo de referencia paso a paso para aplicar cierres por tipología, cierres generales por día y\n        mantenimiento de la tarifa NR. Úsalo como guía de verificación rápida tras cada operación.\n      </p>\n      <a class=\"drive-video-card__btn\"\n         href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15XNJZxf5ZA5MkmFk-qARtXYLslLZi-zk/view?usp=sharing\"\n         target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        ▶️ Ver vídeo en Google Drive\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Miniatura con overlay (Drive genera el thumbnail) -->\n    <a class=\"drive-video-card__thumb\"\n       href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15XNJZxf5ZA5MkmFk-qARtXYLslLZi-zk/view?usp=sharing\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"Abrir vídeo en Google Drive\">\n      <img\n        src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=15XNJZxf5ZA5MkmFk-qARtXYLslLZi-zk\"\n        alt=\"Miniatura vídeo: Demostración de cierres en INVENTORY\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n      <span class=\"drive-video-card__play\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▶</span>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"drive-video-card__note\">Acceso: asegúrate de iniciar sesión con la cuenta del hotel si Drive lo solicita.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- ⬆️ FIN TARJETA DE VÍDEO -->\n<style>\n  .drive-video-card{\n    margin: 18px 0 10px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--ring, #e6eef2);\n    border-radius: 14px;\n    background: linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fbff,#fff);\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(2,6,23,.06);\n    padding: 12px;\n  }\n  .drive-video-card__body{\n    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; gap: 14px; align-items: center;\n  }\n  .drive-video-card__title{ margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #004f6e; }\n  .drive-video-card__desc{ margin: 0 0 10px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.5; }\n  .drive-video-card__btn{\n    display:inline-block; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none;\n    color:#073042; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,146,198,.18) 0%, rgba(0,146,198,.28) 100%);\n    border:1px solid rgba(0,146,198,.35);\n    box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(0,146,198,.15), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.55);\n    transition:transform .12s ease, filter .12s ease;\n  }\n  .drive-video-card__btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); filter: brightness(1.06); }\n  .drive-video-card__thumb{ position:relative; display:block; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #e6eef2; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }\n  .drive-video-card__thumb img{ display:block; width:100%; aspect-ratio:16/9; object-fit:cover; }\n  .drive-video-card__play{\n    position:absolute; inset:0; display:grid; place-items:center; font-size:54px; color:#fff;\n    text-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.35);\n    background: radial-gradient(closest-side, rgba(0,0,0,.22), transparent 70%);\n    transition: transform .12s ease, opacity .12s ease;\n  }\n  .drive-video-card__thumb:hover .drive-video-card__play{ transform:scale(1.04); opacity:.95; }\n  .drive-video-card__note{ margin:8px 4px 0; font-size:.9rem; color:#64748b; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 820px){\n    .drive-video-card__body{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n",
