    "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Descubre el Restaurante y la Cafetería del Hotel Guadiana en Ciudad Real. Cocina gourmet, ambiente elegante y cartas disponibles online.\">\n  <title>Restaurante Hotel Guadiana</title>\n  <style>\n    * {\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    body {\n      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n      background-color: #fff;\n      color: #333;\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n\n    main.container {\n      flex: 1;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 30px;\n      padding: 20px;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .section {\n      flex: 1 1 45%;\n      background: #fff;\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n      transition: transform 0.2s;\n    }\n\n    .section:hover {\n      transform: translateY(-2px);\n    }\n\n    .section-image {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: auto;\n      max-height: 400px;\n      object-fit: cover;\n    }\n\n    .section-info {\n      padding: 1.2rem;\n      background-color: #fafafa;\n    }\n\n    .section-info h2 {\n      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n      text-align: center;\n      color: #b22222;\n      font-size: 1.6rem;\n    }\n\n    .section-info p {\n      line-height: 1.8;\n      font-size: 1rem;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .section-info a {\n      display: inline-block;\n      text-align: center;\n      width: 100%;\n      background-color: #b22222;\n      color: #fff;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      padding: 0.7rem 0;\n      border-radius: 6px;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      font-size: 1rem;\n      transition: background-color 0.3s;\n    }\n\n    .section-info a:hover {\n      background-color: #8b1a1a;\n    }\n\n    footer {\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 1rem;\n      font-size: 0.9rem;\n      color: #666;\n      background-color: #f0f0f0;\n      margin-top: 60px;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .section {\n        flex: 1 1 100%;\n        max-width: 100%;\n      }\n\n      .section-image {\n        max-height: 300px;\n      }\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 600px) {\n      main.container {\n        padding: 10px;\n        gap: 20px;\n      }\n\n      .section-info h2 {\n        font-size: 1.4rem;\n      }\n\n      .section-info p {\n        font-size: 0.95rem;\n      }\n\n      .section-info a {\n        font-size: 0.95rem;\n      }\n    }\n\n    @media (min-width: 1024px) {\n      .section {\n        flex: 1 1 99%;\n        max-width: none;\n      }\n\n      main.container {\n        padding: 40px;\n        gap: 1%;\n      }\n\n      .section-info h2 {\n        font-size: 1.8rem;\n      }\n\n      .section-info p {\n        font-size: 1.1rem;\n      }\n    }\n\n    @media (min-width: 1200px) {\n      .section {\n        flex: 1 1 120%;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <main class=\"container\">\n    <section class=\"section\">\n      <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczPWUJtGdwfZiZr2yRBj7Scyk1s8wNaFUtTshlEhBYLEJjqfYJABi87WkeuXdcvmmkXsRGptFgOfnqJTS92YUVSXHQDDeXzdrq-qqxOuvonS18-mov-yHm6Jn-Ks1JtSt1P9u65k7IsfAswwXuPsA4YX=w895-h599-s-no-gm?authuser=0\" alt=\"Vista del comedor del restaurante del Hotel Guadiana\" class=\"section-image\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n      <div class=\"section-info\">\n        <h2>Restaurante</h2>\n        <p>\n          Bienvenidos al Restaurante Hotel Guadiana, donde hemos preparado una experiencia gourmet con amor y dedicación para deleitar sus sentidos.\n          Descubra platos exquisitos elaborados con ingredientes frescos de la más alta calidad, en un ambiente elegante y acogedor.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://restaurantehotelguadiana.blogspot.com/p/carta-de-restaurane.html\">Ver carta del restaurante</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"section\">\n      <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczPhMptYUWA-tBQ4EpJEHJQyYaQt55yL3QurARvUpcqHsm4FGzwiHRLxEjmZbq2Q-V5WwARPGrOjCdAvqoDHLiaBh1FTFAZymMlk0tQIMIbscOZ33kcXZQUgsZZoWgr0KhxlV76RJ_05hiyO4Tnp9pHJ=w799-h599-s-no-gm?authuser=0\" alt=\"Interior de la cafetería del Hotel Guadiana\" class=\"section-image\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n      <div class=\"section-info\">\n        <h2>Cafetería</h2>\n        <p>\n          ¡Saborea nuestra propuesta gourmet en un ambiente relajado y acogedor en nuestra cafetería!\n          Disfruta de la misma calidad y sabor que en nuestro restaurante, pero en un entorno más informal.\n          Perfecta para un desayuno, un almuerzo ligero o una merienda deliciosa.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://restaurantehotelguadiana.blogspot.com/p/carta-de-cafeteria-2025-estilos.html\">Ver carta de la cafetería</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n  <footer>\n    © 2025 Restaurante Hotel Guadiana\n  </footer>\n</body>\n\n</html>\n",
    "published": "2025-04-29T08:50:00.001Z",
