    "title": "Visita histórica de Ciudad Real",
    "section": "",
    "content": "<div class=\"separator\"><div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;\"><div class=\"separator\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><h1 class=\"entry-title\" id=\"i4t-id-r0kxb8901\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1em; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\">La mejor forma de conocer Ciudad Real</h1></div></div></div></div><div><div><span face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #666666;\"><div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://turismo.ciudadreal.es/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VISITA-HISTORICA-2023-980x1386.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1386\" data-original-width=\"980\" src=\"https://turismo.ciudadreal.es/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/VISITA-HISTORICA-2023-980x1386.jpg\" /></a></div><br /><span face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\" style=\"color: #666666;\"><a href=\"https://turismo.ciudadreal.es/que-visitar-en-ciudad-real/visitas-guiadas/\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"129\" data-original-width=\"300\" height=\"129\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj-u1DXlQUrbfePwCvYgovfSHL8eKBZXPqbkeFTnVIVCTkRVjClhv6JO-sJIoGPmhchRximTDF5DMWb8-1elf2pj1LN5SPwBMSxT9b_z716gTOLOLfd1ZQigEEov-AAZMSg67JOhN_AVkrnPNkQD4CAoq8S_ShXjSi7Y6HdIwxfOPlD72Vf4DChv9aLGns/s1600/RESERVA-AQUI.png\" width=\"300\" /></a></span></div><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /></span></span><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiHKDu6u5BdTVahHz0y74Tp0Y9z4g8FnbGt-uTiRTB9Hvuo1-7H8Kr-GPLtnjie4adGqhU7_pRZbp0IzJIPaDF39mBoKHXzfWSBspm9gqp92SCQXSGZoa88BDjEHQ4gsfGHRcH9RpxW5HRAoN8yMDhD9YlESCFvd7yYfz_ezQq0XMngAusNS-tlgieiIlE/s2205/guadiana%20logo_P%C3%A1gina%20serco.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"989\" data-original-width=\"2205\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiHKDu6u5BdTVahHz0y74Tp0Y9z4g8FnbGt-uTiRTB9Hvuo1-7H8Kr-GPLtnjie4adGqhU7_pRZbp0IzJIPaDF39mBoKHXzfWSBspm9gqp92SCQXSGZoa88BDjEHQ4gsfGHRcH9RpxW5HRAoN8yMDhD9YlESCFvd7yYfz_ezQq0XMngAusNS-tlgieiIlE/w400-h180/guadiana%20logo_P%C3%A1gina%20serco.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><br /></div></div>",
