    "title": "Escapadas con Spa",
    "section": "",
    "content": "<br /><br /><br /><br /><div class=\"separator\"><div style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.gstatic.com/consumer/images/icons/1x/directions_walk_blue900_24dp.png\" />25 min 1,8 km&nbsp; &nbsp;<img border=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.gstatic.com/consumer/images/icons/1x/directions_car_grey800_24dp.png\" style=\"text-align: center;\" />5 min 2,0 km&nbsp;</div><div style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">(de Sercotel Guadiana)</span></div></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTmAmTUMqXAmmjjmurBo2TpKWMk3NkKrp2QuA&amp;s\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"225\" data-original-width=\"225\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTmAmTUMqXAmmjjmurBo2TpKWMk3NkKrp2QuA&amp;s\" width=\"200\" /></a></div><br /><p><br /></p>",
