    "title": "ESCAPADA A TU AIRE - Visitas guiadas Arco del Torreón y galerías",
    "section": "",
    "content": "<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #073763; font-family: verdana; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;\">Visitas guiadas Arco del Torreón y galerías</span></h2><blockquote style=\"border: none; margin: 0 0 0 40px; padding: 0px;\"><blockquote style=\"border: none; margin: 0 0 0 40px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; text-align: justify; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi1io9qws3ldkcgo6327O6numEqg4JaqXYBtjxddvm8zACs2oFsb49Wc0briDp-XVJATq0pIiSzROHM-gQs1Xs5-6k-finVodub4T4jrDfvApwmGRdPv_dW23_Nln98Awfrl2zxNiOK5Mo/s1080/1614770857_741731_1614771084_noticia_normal.jpg\" style=\"background-color: transparent; clear: left; display: inline; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"721\" data-original-width=\"1080\" height=\"268\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi1io9qws3ldkcgo6327O6numEqg4JaqXYBtjxddvm8zACs2oFsb49Wc0briDp-XVJATq0pIiSzROHM-gQs1Xs5-6k-finVodub4T4jrDfvApwmGRdPv_dW23_Nln98Awfrl2zxNiOK5Mo/w400-h268/1614770857_741731_1614771084_noticia_normal.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></span></a></span></span></p></blockquote></blockquote><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;Horario:</span>&nbsp;11:00, 12:00 y 13:00 horas,</span><span style=\"background: transparent; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; font-size: 16px;\">los últimos domingos de cada mes.</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;\">Punto&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: transparent; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\">de encuentro:</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: verdana; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;Arco del Torreón</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #666666; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b style=\"background: transparent; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span></span></span></span></b></p><!--more--><p></p><p style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b style=\"background: transparent; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color: #666666;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"color: red;\">&nbsp; ** Importante **</span></span></span></span></b><br /><br />Las personas con movilidad reducida deberán tener en cuenta las escaleras de la bajada a la galería .<br />Se ruega que avisen con suficiente antelación si no pueden asistir.<br />Uso obligatorio de mascarilla</p>",
